#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "2. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 17. Pāraṅgamasutta → apārasuttaṃ (bj) | pāraṅgāmi (pts1)
msgctxt "sn46.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Pāraṅgamasutta "
msgstr "17. Going to the Far Shore "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.17:1.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhikkhave, bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when these seven awakening factors are developed and cultivated they lead to going from the near shore to the far shore. "

msgctxt "sn46.17:1.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.17:1.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo—"
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.17:1.4"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, satta bojjhaṅgā bhāvitā bahulīkatā apārā pāraṃ gamanāya saṃvattantīti. "
msgstr "These seven awakening factors, when developed and cultivated, lead to going from the near shore to the far shore. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.82, sc2
msgctxt "sn46.17:2.1"
msgid "Appakā te manussesu, "
msgstr "Few are those among humans "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:2.2"
msgid "ye janā pāragāmino; "
msgstr "who cross to the far shore. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:2.3"
msgid "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā, "
msgstr "The rest just run "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:2.4"
msgid "tīramevānudhāvati. "
msgstr "around on the near shore. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn46.17:3.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho sammadakkhāte, "
msgstr "When the teaching is well explained, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:3.2"
msgid "dhamme dhammānuvattino; "
msgstr "those who practice accordingly "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:3.3"
msgid "Te janā pāramessanti, "
msgstr "are the ones who will cross over "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:3.4"
msgid "maccudheyyaṃ suduttaraṃ. "
msgstr "Death’s domain so hard to pass. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn46.17:4.1"
msgid "Kaṇhaṃ dhammaṃ vippahāya, "
msgstr "Rid of dark qualities, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:4.2"
msgid "sukkaṃ bhāvetha paṇḍito; "
msgstr "an astute person should develop the bright. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:4.3"
msgid "Okā anokamāgamma, "
msgstr "Leaving home behind "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:4.4"
msgid "viveke yattha dūramaṃ. "
msgstr "for the seclusion so hard to enjoy, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "sn46.17:5.1"
msgid "Tatrābhiratimiccheyya, "
msgstr "you should try to find delight there, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:5.2"
msgid "hitvā kāme akiñcano; "
msgstr "having left behind sensual pleasures. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:5.3"
msgid "Pariyodapeyya attānaṃ, "
msgstr "With no possessions, an astute person "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:5.4"
msgid "cittaklesehi paṇḍito. "
msgstr "should cleanse themselves of mental corruptions. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.1"
msgid "Yesaṃ sambodhiyaṅgesu, "
msgstr "And those whose minds are rightly developed "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.2"
msgid "sammā cittaṃ subhāvitaṃ; "
msgstr "in the awakening factors; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.3"
msgid "Ādānappaṭinissagge, "
msgstr "letting go of attachments, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.4"
msgid "anupādāya ye ratā; "
msgstr "they delight in not grasping. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.5"
msgid "Khīṇāsavā jutimanto, "
msgstr "With defilements ended, brilliant, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.6"
msgid "te loke parinibbutā”ti. "
msgstr "they are extinguished in this world.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.17:6.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
